## 📋 **TODO Resolution Workflow**

### Before Starting Work
1. **Check Priority**: Focus on Critical → High → Medium
2. **Estimate Impact**: Consider user-facing vs internal improvements
3. **Plan Dependencies**: Some TODOs depend on others being resolved first

### When Adding New TODOs
```typescript
// ✅ GOOD: Descriptive with context
// TODO: Implement retry logic for failed API calls - affects user experience
// IMPACT: Users see errors without retry attempts
// ESTIMATE: 2-3 hours

// ❌ BAD: Vague without context  
// TODO: fix this
```

### TODO Comment Standards
```typescript
// Format: TODO: [Description] - [Impact/Context]
// Optional: IMPACT: [Business/Technical impact]
// Optional: ESTIMATE: [Time estimate]
// Optional: DEPENDS: [Other TODOs that must be resolved first]
```

