## 🛠️ **Tools and Automation**

### Recommended VS Code Extensions
- **TODO Highlight**: Highlights TODO comments in code
- **TODO Tree**: Provides sidebar view of all TODOs
- **GitLens**: Shows TODO history and ownership

### Git Hooks (Recommended)
```bash
# Pre-commit hook to prevent new Critical TODOs
#!/bin/sh
if git diff --cached | grep -i TODO.*CRITICAL\|FIXME.*CRITICAL; then
  echo ❌ Critical TODOs detected. Please resolve before committing.
  exit 1
fi
```

### Search Commands
```bash
# Find all TODOs
bun run grep -r TODO\|FIXME\|XXX\|HACK src/

# Find Critical TODOs
bun run grep -r TODO.*CRITICAL\|FIXME.*CRITICAL src/

# Count TODOs by file
bun run grep -rc TODO\|FIXME src/ | grep -v :0
```

